OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,FAdolescence made history at the Bafta
OL,7,FTelevision Awards on Sunday, scooping
OL,8,Ffour awards - the most won by a single
OL,9,FTV series in the main ceremony.
OL,11,FThe hard-hitting Netflix show, which
OL,12,Fsparked a national debate after its
OL,13,Frelease last year, was named best
OL,14,Flimited drama, while stars Stephen
OL,15,FGraham, Christine Tremarco and Owen
OL,16,FCooper all won awards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
