PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778505068
OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,FGraham was named best leading actor,
OL,7,FTremarco won the supporting actress
OL,8,Fprize, and Cooper took supporting
OL,9,Factor, as the drama completed its
OL,10,Fwinning streak through awards season.
OL,12,FGraham, who co-wrote the script with
OL,13,FJack Thorne, has won a string of
OL,14,Fawards for his performance in the
OL,15,FNetflix series, including an Emmy and
OL,16,Fa Golden Globe, but had never won a
OL,17,FBafta.
OL,19,F"Nice one Bafta, this is lovely," he
OL,20,Fsaid on stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
