OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778505068
OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,F"When I was a kid, I watched a telly
OL,7,Fprogramme called Scully, written by
OL,8,FAlan Bleasdale, and it had the
OL,9,Fwonderful Drew Schofield in it and he
OL,10,Flived across the road from my nana's
OL,11,Fhouse, so he showed me that I could be
OL,12,Fon the telly.
OL,14,F"He was my inspiration. So for any
OL,15,Fother young kid, no matter where
OL,16,Fyou're from, anything is possible.
OL,18,F"We are all people that have done
OL,19,Fthat, we get to do what we love, which
OL,20,Fis different.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
