PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778505068
OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,F"We're not digging holes, we're not
OL,7,Fdigging ditches, we're not saving
OL,8,Flives, but we have the opportunity to
OL,9,Ftell the human condition, and we have
OL,10,Fthe obligation to tell beautiful
OL,11,Fstories and we need to keep that
OL,12,Fgoing."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
