OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778505068
OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,FAdolescence tells the story of 13-year-
OL,7,Fold Jamie - played by up-and-coming
OL,8,Factor Owen Cooper, who has proved
OL,9,Funbeatable through awards season - as
OL,10,Fhe is accused of murdering his female
OL,11,Fclassmate.
OL,13,FThe show sparked a national debate
OL,14,Fafter its release last year, and in
OL,15,Fthe wake of its impact, Netflix agreed
OL,16,Fto allow schools to show the series to
OL,17,Fpupils for free as a learning resource.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
