OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778505068
OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,FCooper, 16, became the youngest ever
OL,7,Fwinner of the award for best
OL,8,Fsupporting actor for his part in the
OL,9,Fhit drama.
OL,11,F"A year ago, I was presenting an award
OL,12,Fand now I'm collecting one. This is a
OL,13,Fbit mad," he said.
OL,15,F"In the words of John Lennon, you
OL,16,Fwon't get anything unless you have the
OL,17,Fvision to imagine it.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
