PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778505068
OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,F"So in my eyes, I think you only need
OL,7,Fthree things to succeed: one, you need
OL,8,Fan obsession; two, you need a dream;
OL,9,Fand three, you need The Beatles."
OL,11,FElsewhere, Celebrity Traitors won the
OL,12,Faward for best reality, and Alan
OL,13,FCarr's treacherous victory picked up
OL,14,Fthe memorable moment prize.
OL,16,FCollecting the award, he said: "Was I
OL,17,Fgood? Was I really? Or were the other
OL,18,Fcelebrities just thick?
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]xD@`OU
