OL,3,CAdolescence makes history at Baftas
OL,4,Cwith four wins
OL,6,FGaza: Doctors Under Attack, the
OL,7,Fdocumentary commissioned and then
OL,8,Fshelved by the BBC over impartiality
OL,9,Fconcerns and later aired by Channel 4,
OL,10,Fwon the current affairs Bafta.
OL,12,FDuring his speech on stage, executive
OL,13,Fproducer Ben de Pear referred to the
OL,14,Ffact the BBC airs the ceremony on
OL,15,Fdelay, saying: "Finally, just a
OL,16,Fquestion for the BBC: given you
OL,17,Fdropped our film, will you drop us
OL,18,Ffrom the Bafta screening later
OL,19,Ftonight?"
OL,26,@wD@POU{D@IO]
